## Project Overview
This project analyzes customer behavior using SQL and MySQL.

## Dataset
- Customer Behavior Dataset
- Cleaned using Python (Pandas)
- Imported into MySQL

## Database Tables
- customer_behavior
- events
- products
- users

## SQL Analyses
1. JOIN Queries
2. Funnel Conversion Analysis
3. Abandoned Products
4. Repeat Purchase Analysis
5. Average Order Value (AOV)
6. Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)

## SQL Optimization
Indexes were created on:
- user_id
- product_id
- event_type
- event_time

## Tools Used
- Python
- Jupyter Notebook
- MySQL Workbench
- GitHub
